{"tid":1308460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來獅球嘜都只係表現不錯 呢隻樣衰衰嘅芥花籽油先係表現最好","createTime":"2019-07-12T01:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T16:25:53.000Z","uid":23707,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e4046d0f60fb3649877a2fd0beb8395bb5e09d2c","tid":1308460,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:47:09.000Z","msg":"[HK01] 消委會檢測市面上60款常見食油的重金屬、致癌物、塑化劑、污染物等，全數樣本被驗出最少殘餘一種化學物質。記者比較各樣本，發現內地製造的「御萬家濃香花生油」雖價錢相宜，900毫升平均只29元，但同時「成份最齊」，除了污染物氯丙二醇遠較其他樣本為高，還含有兩款塑化劑、致癌物苯並[a]芘和環氧丙醇、黃曲霉毒素、芥酸和抗氧化劑。<br />\n<br />\n御萬家的代理商回覆消委會的檢測結果指，會與供應商詳細瞭解及跟進有關食油配方及精煉程序，並積極研究改良方法，為消費者提供更高品質的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n馬拉芥花籽油表現最好 僅貴御萬家1元<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">來自馬來西亞的「萬歲芥花籽油」則表現最好</span>，多項檢測合格，僅檢出有少量環氧丙醇，900毫升平均價格是30元，僅貴表現最差的「御萬家濃香花生油」1元；「本地薑」表現亦不俗，香港「獅球嘜」的芥花籽油和粟米油都通過多項檢測，只檢出環氧丙醇，含量僅稍高出表現最好的「萬歲芥花籽油」。價錢方面「獅球嘜芥花籽油」900毫升平均價格只需23元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjEAYQL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjEAYQL.png&h=17fc9a21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHuEF4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHuEF4T.png&h=3f079d93&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n平時買油見到呢隻油會覺得咁老土以為係支那嘢 望都唔望吓<br />\n但係放工就立即去買桶放喺屋企, 用哂屋企嘅存貨就轉用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XWPiQb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XWPiQb.png&h=db5a6b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獅球嘜都只係表現不錯, 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7542c1c011487be7cf6a35f72b50fcd6c431a412","tid":1308460,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:51:05.000Z","msg":"大家放工做孝順仔<br />\n買返幾桶返屋企<br />\n同阿媽講返呢隻油先係最靚<br />\n叫佢班師奶朋友一齊轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40231d57d3ff8300be051e782def5a4b727ba335","tid":1308460,"uid":19712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"佳之選果然佳之選 最多料"},{"pid":"a1f1d987b0bf8751d6363b0bc2a47de1c7c79af3","tid":1308460,"uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"40231d57d3ff8300be051e782def5a4b727ba335","tid":1308460,"uid":19712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"佳之選果然佳之選 最多料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:52:13.000Z","msg":"落足料都收你咁平 其實賺咗"},{"pid":"369b47c210ef4fc03681fafa98c874c45ce3466e","tid":1308460,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:52:58.000Z","msg":"呢隻賣緊cctvb廣告"},{"pid":"467a6ea8f59bb899fff1c082812f6d267005386f","tid":1308460,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"369b47c210ef4fc03681fafa98c874c45ce3466e","tid":1308460,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:52:58.000Z","msg":"呢隻賣緊cctvb廣告"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"無留意, 有咁嘅事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1470049e217f71033148993f9fffd4f5d6823443","tid":1308460,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467a6ea8f59bb899fff1c082812f6d267005386f","tid":1308460,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"369b47c210ef4fc03681fafa98c874c45ce3466e","tid":1308460,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:52:58.000Z","msg":"呢隻賣緊cctvb廣告"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"無留意, 有咁嘅事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:53:56.000Z","msg":"不過獅球嘜都有啦"},{"pid":"0b11b5e1e4d674c8de345b83fadaf73544059c79","tid":1308460,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467a6ea8f59bb899fff1c082812f6d267005386f","tid":1308460,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":